\prod_{\substack{j=0\\ j \neq i}}^{n} \frac{n+1-j}{i-j}
\prod_{\substack{j=0\\ j \neq i}}^{n} \frac{n+1-j}{i-j} = \prod_{j=0}^{i-1} \frac{n+1-j}{i-j} \times \prod_{j=i+1}^{n} \frac{n+1-j}{i-j}
